  m_Name: GSWGA_Course_3_Lesson_3_Q3
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionData
  question: "Which prompting technique best matches the given scenario?\nA social
    media team asks the LLM to summarize their monthly engagement statistics, but
    doesn\u2019t specify the format or focus."
  answers:
  - Define the task clearly
  - Be specific
  - Include examples
  - Use simple and direct language
  maxSelections: 1
  correctAnswerIndices: 01000000
  correctMessage: "Including specific details, such as a focus on likes and shares
    or using bullet points, helps narrow the LLM\u2019s output to match expectations."
  incorrectMessage: "Not quite. Consider how adding specifics to the prompt can refine
    the output to meet the team\u2019s needs."
